@startuml DATA-LINEAGE-001
!pragma layout smetana
title DATA-LINEAGE-001 — Spatial evidence identity, lineage and attribution
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

rectangle "Source registry record\nsourceId + terms + readiness" as Registry
rectangle "Dataset version\ndatasetId + version + checksum" as Dataset
rectangle "Feature envelope\nfeatureKey + source aliases +\nprovenance + geometry quality" as Feature
rectangle "Layer catalogue\nlayerKey + fallbackLayerKey +\nattributionIds + reviewState" as Layer
rectangle "Activation result\neffective source/layers + reason" as Activation
rectangle "Map feature / analysis target\nstatus labels + dataset identity" as MapFeature
rectangle "Selection lineage\nproviderFeatureId != sourceRecordId" as Selection
rectangle "Visible attribution payload\nonly visible layer/provider records" as Attribution
rectangle "Analysis / report evidence\nsource snapshot + caveat" as Evidence

Registry --> Dataset
Dataset --> Feature
Dataset --> Layer
Feature --> Activation : bundle availability/checksum
Layer --> Activation : eligibility + fallback
Activation --> MapFeature : activated feature only
Feature --> Selection
Layer --> Selection
MapFeature --> Evidence
Selection --> Evidence
Activation --> Attribution : active + visible layers
Attribution --> Evidence

note bottom of Feature
Controlled B2A fixture has invented, non-real geometry.
No OSM/Overture provider geometry is inferred from attribution tests.
end note
@enduml
